{
  "stem": "8.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[TONE]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I left off that we were leaving Wiesau.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I heard later that this camp commander was later reprimanded for being too soft on the prisoners and was taken back to Germany and I think was punished.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Also at this point-- at this place in Wiesau, I had a cousin who was pregnant, who we hoped that she could have a baby in the camp.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But she was not allowed to have a baby, and she was promised she could deliver a baby in another camp.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they took her to Gross-Rosen, which we didn't realize at that time they also had gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she-- she was killed there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Anyway, we-- we got back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We-- we-- we got back to the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were taken to Reichenbach-Langenbielau.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I think they were so close to each other that it was a hyphenated station.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was southeast of Breslau and a little bit east-- no, southwest of Breslau and east of the place where we had been before.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "At this place, probably the most difficult part of our camp experience, maybe because we had been already for awhile because our resistance was getting low or because the circumstances became much more difficult-- when we were in Auschwitz, of course, because of our naivete and our reserve yet, we somehow did not perceive it, the enormity of the problem.",
      "word_count": 60
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But when we were here already, we saw how little hope there was for our survival.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were housed in a place in Reichenbach, which were cement blocks-- made of cement blocks, barracks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But there no-- there were no beds, no platforms to sleep on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We slept on the floor, on the cement floor.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There were windows there without any glass.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And this was wintertime.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
